            class="text-cAccent"
            href="/projects">Projects</a
          > page. You can view an assortment of the software I've used below:
        </p>
        <ul
          data-aos="fade-left"
          data-aos-once="true"
          data-aos-duration="500"
          class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 bg-mid p-4 mb-6 rounded-lg shadow-xl"
        >
          <Skill
            text="FL Studio"
            image={icFLStudio}
            link="https://www.image-line.com/"
          />
          <Skill
            text="Blender"
            image={icBlender}
            link="https://www.blender.org/"
          />
          <Skill
            text="GameMaker"
            image={icGamemaker}
