          data-aos-duration="500"
          class="text-4xl font-bold"
        >
          Pages üìú
        </h3>
        <p data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-once="true" data-aos-duration="500">
          You can view the various works I've created using the links below, or
          the navigation items at the top. You may also contact me through an
          email form if you'd like.
        </p>
        <ul data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-once="true" data-aos-duration="500">
          <li class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="/web-apps">üì¶ Web Apps</a>
            <a href="/projects">üé® Projects</a>
